<h2>How to Add a To Do from the Dashboard</h2>

<p>General to do:  <strong>[your to do text][enter]</strong>

<p>To do associated with an active project:  
<strong>[project short name]---[your to do text][enter]</strong>  
Note that the short name is separated from the to do text by three hyphens (3 x -).


<p>To do associated with an active project and assigned to a user: 
<strong>[project short name]---[assignee username]---[your to do text][enter]</strong>  
Again, note that the delimeter is seried of three hyphens.

